question: What is the label of the class "http://rdf.rhea-db.org/DirectionalReaction" in Rhea database?
What is the label for the class "http://rdf.rhea-db.org/ReactionParticipant" in the Rhea database?
What is the status of the 'Approved' entity in Rhea Database?
sparql_query:
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://rdf.rhea-db.org/>

SELECT ?label
WHERE {
  rdf:Approved rdfs:subClassOf ?status .
  ?status rdfs:label ?label .
}
